<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-82-1437 </DOCNO><TEXT>The updated handbook lists the most important environmental authoritiesof the State and Laender, the European environmental authorities, associationsand societies in the field of environmental protection, as well as agenciesunder section 26 of the Federal Act for the Protection against Nuisancesmeasuring air-pollutant emission, and nuisances resulting from air pollutants.A detailed market survey again covers the treatment of contaminated soiland/or soil protection. There is a catalogue of groups of products witha survey for rapid information, and a list of suppliers.</TEXT></DOC>